#. <section class="sutta" id="sn47.41"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.41:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.41:0.2"
msgid "5. Amatavagga"
msgstr "5. The Deathless"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.41:0.3"
msgid "41. Amatasutta"
msgstr "41. The Deathless"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.41:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn47.41:1.2"
msgid "“Catūsu, bhikkhave, satipaṭṭhānesu suppatiṭṭhitacittā viharatha."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, you should meditate with your mind firmly established in the "
"four kinds of mindfulness meditation."

msgctxt "sn47.41:1.3"
msgid "Mā vo amataṃ panassa."
msgstr "Don’t let the deathless escape you."

msgctxt "sn47.41:1.4"
msgid "Katamesu catūsu?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn47.41:1.5"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, "
"vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, "
"aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn47.41:1.6"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings …"

msgctxt "sn47.41:1.7"
msgid "citte … pe …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn47.41:1.8"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke "
"abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn47.41:1.9"
msgid "Imesu, bhikkhave, catūsu satipaṭṭhānesu suppatiṭṭhitacittā viharatha."
msgstr ""
"You should meditate with your mind firmly established in the four kinds of "
"mindfulness meditation."

msgctxt "sn47.41:1.10"
msgid "Mā vo amataṃ panassā”ti."
msgstr "Don’t let the deathless escape you.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.41:1.11"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
